antity of generated patch candidates of\nthe 16 open-source repair tools for Java programs. The experiments are\ncarefully conducted under the same fault localization configurations to limit\nbiases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Aug 2020 14:47:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-04"}
